// Each of these tests were generated by a simple C application made with the
//   original xo[ro]shiro authors' source code files.
//
// Regardless of _how_ the PRNG is seeded, what's important is that the deterministic behaviors are the same.
//   After all, this isn't a cryptographic generator or hash.
//
module xorshift_tests @test;

import std::math::random;

